data.description: You will love the magical charm of this fully renovated stone Tudor home on a spacious, quiet street. The great room is sure to be a favorite gathering place with its hardwood floors, gorgeous wood ceiling beams and recently converted gas fireplace. There is a stunning vintage fireplace in the primary bedroom suite that can be easily be converted into gas. This home is virtually maintenance-free with a new HVAC system, newer roof, windows, driveway and exterior paint. The sunroom in back looks out on the perfect outdoor gathering space surrounded by a new wood privacy fence. You'll find plenty of storage space in the basement and a lovely, carpeted rec room. Washer, dryer, Ring doorbell, camera and hardware all stay!
